com.vector.cfg.gen.core.bswmdmodel.groovy.extensions

Class BswmdModelExtensions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vector.cfg.gen.core.bswmdmodel.groovy.extensions.BswmdModelExtensions

  • @PublishedApi(value=ADDITIONS_ALLOWED)
 @PublishedApiDomain(value=AUTOMATION_IF)
public final class BswmdModelExtensions
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides extension methods for BswmdModel object like GIModelObject and other helper classes like optionals. The bswmdModel methods are the same as in the API interface IBswmdModelApiEntryPoint.

    (c) Copyright Vctr Informatik GmbH. All Rights Reserved.

      • executeWithCreationModelView

        @PublishedMethod
public static <T extends GIModelObject> void executeWithCreationModelView(T bswmdModelObject,
                                                                                            @DelegatesTo(strategy=1)
                                                                                            groovy.lang.Closure<?> code)
        The method executeWithCreationModelView(Closure)} executes the Closure code under visibility of the GIModelObject.getCreationModelView() of this GIModelObject. You could use this method, if you want to return an object from this operation. 

         
 GIModelObject myModelObject = ...;

 ReturnType returnVal = myModelObject.executeWithCreationModelView {
   // do some operations
  }
        Type Parameters:
        T - the generic type of the BswmdModelObject
        Parameters:
        bswmdModelObject - the bswmd model object
        code - the code to execute
        See Also:
        IModelViewManager.executeWithModelView(IModelView)
